{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420062331","title":"Internal quality adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery","desc":"Fowler: untuk internal quality, hubungan biaya-kecepatan terbalik; kualitas tinggi mempercepat delivery karena mengurangi cruft.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","martin-fowler","internal-quality"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"cbb86755b9eb00693a11e154a1677798","updated":1776683200348,"created":1776683200348,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.martin-fowler","alias":"martin-fowler","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.martin-fowler"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.internal-quality","alias":"internal-quality","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.internal-quality"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1129},"end":{"line":20,"column":50,"offset":1176},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420062120","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1254},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1279},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062120"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062331","id":"zettel.20260420062331","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420061530","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1343},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1368},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061530"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":3,"offset":4372},"end":{"line":56,"column":28,"offset":4397},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062331"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420085220","id":"zettel.20260420085220","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1251},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1276},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062331"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":3,"offset":4537},"end":{"line":63,"column":28,"offset":4562},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420062331"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"internal-quality-adalah-infrastruktur-kecepatan-delivery\">Internal quality adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#internal-quality-adalah-infrastruktur-kecepatan-delivery\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"This situation is counter to our usual experience. We are used to something that is 'high quality' as something that costs more. For some aspects of software, such as the user-experience, this can be true. But when it comes to the architecture, and other aspects of internal quality, this relationship is reversed. High internal quality leads to faster delivery of new features, because there is less cruft to get in the way.\"</p>\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/architecture/\">https://martinfowler.com/architecture/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Paragraf ini membalik intuisi umum bahwa kualitas tinggi selalu berarti biaya lebih besar.</li>\n<li>Untuk internal quality, termasuk arsitektur, kualitas tinggi justru mengurangi cruft dan mempercepat delivery.</li>\n<li>Itu membuat internal quality jadi infrastruktur kecepatan, bukan hiasan engineering.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Jika internal quality rendah, setiap fitur baru harus menerobos jaringan coupling dan ketidakjelasan.</li>\n<li>Manajemen harus memandang investasi pada internal quality sebagai cara menjaga produktivitas jangka panjang.</li>\n<li>Arsitektur sehat artinya mengurangi hambatan cognitive load dan membuat perubahan lebih mudah.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.internal-quality-is-speed\">Kualitas internal adalah infrastruktur kecepatan delivery</a> — literatur Fowler yang menekankan internal quality dan kecepatan delivery</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420062120\">Cruft adalah utang kebingungan yang memperlambat perubahan</a> — cruft adalah utang kebingungan yang memperlambat perubahan</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061530\">Architecture adalah seni memilah keputusan penting</a> — architecture adalah seni memilah keputusan penting</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">martin-fowler (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">internal-quality (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420085220\">Shortcut kualitas adalah pinjaman dari masa depan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}